/All-Together-Now-lineup@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/All-Together-Now-lineup@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/All-Together-Now-lineup@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/All-Together-Now-lineup@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/All-Together-Now-lineup@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/All-Together-Now-lineup@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> All Together Now 2025 的第一批表演艺术家已经共享，其中<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">Fontaines DC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bicep">Bicep</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cmat">CMAT</a>领衔。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/fontaines-d-c-romance-review-3784445">Fontaines DC –“浪漫”评论：淘汰赛，时间终结的精神歌曲</a></strong></li></ul><p>今天（11 月 21 日）宣布，明年的音乐节将第六次回归，地点为爱尔兰的 Curraghmore 庄园。</p><p>门票于 7 月 31 日至 8 月 3 日期间举行，第一批门票于 8 月上线，并以创纪录的速度售空。现在，在下周四（11 月 28 日）上午 9 点“第二阶段”门票发售之前，组织者已经分享了第一批将要表演的艺术家。</p><p>此次活动的主角将是获得<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美</a>提名的爱尔兰本土乐队 Fontaines DC，他们将登上 Curraghmore 舞台并演唱他们广受好评的最新专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/fontaines-d-c-romance-review-3784445">Romance</a> 》中的热门歌曲。</p><p>这次亮相是在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/grian-chatten">Grian Chatten</a>及其合作者度过了重要的一年之后，迄今为止，他们已经<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/fontaines-dc-live-at-reading-festival-2024-setlist-photos-3786740">在雷丁和利兹 2024 年举办了大型演出</a>，并获得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplays-chris-martin-on-how-fontaines-dc-remind-him-you-can-never-phone-it-in-3800192">酷玩乐队克里斯·马丁</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elton-john-fontaines-d-c-are-the-best-band-out-there-at-the-moment-3795882">埃尔顿·约翰</a>的高度赞扬。</p><p>加入他们的还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-kiwanuka">迈克尔·基瓦努卡 (Michael Kiwanuka</a> )，他即将发行他期待已久的新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/michael-kiwanuka-announces-small-changes-uk-european-2025-tour-tickets-3799496">“Small Changes”</a> 。 All Together 的演出将是他 2025 年在爱尔兰的唯一一场演出。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DCoR0BZMs_0/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C